      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOVING JESS (4) wasn't far away at the finish when 5th and beaten only 3 lengths (17.18) at this track. Can bounce back. MISS RAINMAKER (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (19.94) at this track behind Blue Bullet in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to be in this for a long way. NEVER GIVING UP (3) has her first outing without a trial but profiles nicely for this. Expected to feature on debut. MIDNIGHT MADNESS (8) is a newcomer from the Patrick Gainey kennel. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Profiles nicely but market best guide to ability.",
